{"type":"message","id":"e254bbb1","parentId":"4396fb31","timestamp":"2026-03-03T10:04:46.049Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_tlma8oqtx0rw_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"financial news API latest market\",\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub.news.retrieve.v1.2e72ea5d\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News\",\n      \"description\": \"Get latest market news.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"category\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"This parameter can be 1 of the following values <code>general, forex, crypto, merger</code>.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"minId\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Use this field to get only news after this ID. Default to 0\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"category\": \"general\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"financialmodelingprep.symbol.change.list.v1.9e6d7ee1\",\n      \"name\": \"Stock Symbol Changes\",\n      \"description\": \"Stay informed about the latest stock symbol changes due to mergers, acquisitions, stock splits, and name changes.\",\n      \"provider_description\": \"FMP offers a stock market data API covers real-time stock prices, historical prices and market news to stock fundamentals and company information. We provide one of the most accurate financial data available on the market. You can get historical prices, fundamental data, insider transactions, and much more that goes back 30 years in history.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg