nothing to push, and maybe add a note about the Finnhub issue.\n\nActually, the right approach is: there's no valid data to push (Finnhub not working + no heat metric found), so I should reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\n\n\nI'll acknowledge the task couldn't be completed and return HEARTBEAT_OK.","thinkingSignature":"e5a9cd8ce20706bcc0c37f5020bd9bc0137726905210650d706250149e26d475"},{"type":"text","text":"我测试了QVeris的Finnhub财经新闻工具，发现存在参数传递问题（即使正确传递category参数也报错\"缺少必需的查询参数\"）。同时，测试了其他财经新闻API：\n\n1. **EODHD财经新闻** - 有情感分析(polarity: -1到1)，但不是\"热度\"指标\n2. **X热门财经话题** - 有互动数据(点赞/转发/曝光)，可作为热度参考\n\nFinnhub新闻API在QVeris上无法正常工作，且未找到\"热度≥80\"的具体指标。建议检查QVeris的Finnhub工具配置或考虑使用其他数据源。\n\nHEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":30855,"output":623,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45462,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772532359045}}
